OL,3,CGovernment introduces law to clear
OL,4,Cvictims of Post Office scandal
OL,6,FThe proposed Post Office (Horizon
OL,7,FSystem) Offences Bill "marks an
OL,8,Fimportant step forward in finally
OL,9,Fclearing" the names of hundreds of
OL,10,Fwronged branch managers who have had
OL,11,Ftheir lives "callously torn apart",
OL,12,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said.
