OL,3,CGovernment introduces law to clear
OL,4,Cvictims of Post Office scandal
OL,6,FThose with overturned convictions will
OL,7,Freceive an interim payment with the
OL,8,Foption of immediately taking a fixed
OL,9,Fand final offer of #600,000, according
OL,10,Fto No 10.
OL,12,FMr Sunak said: "I want to pay tribute
OL,13,Fto all the postmasters who have shown
OL,14,Fsuch courage and perseverance in their
OL,15,Ffierce campaign for justice, and to
OL,16,Fthose who tragically won't see the
OL,17,Fjustice they deserve.
