OL,3,CGovernment introduces law to clear
OL,4,Cvictims of Post Office scandal
OL,6,F"While I know that nothing can make up
OL,7,Ffor what they've been through, today's
OL,8,Flegislation marks an important step
OL,9,Fforward in finally clearing their
OL,10,Fnames.
OL,12,F"We owe it to the victims of this
OL,13,Fscandal who have had their lives and
OL,14,Flivelihoods callously torn apart, to
OL,15,Fdeliver the justice they've fought so
OL,16,Flong and hard for, and to ensure
OL,17,Fnothing like this ever happens again."
