OL,3,CGovernment introduces law to clear
OL,4,Cvictims of Post Office scandal
OL,6,FThe government will also bring forward
OL,7,F"enhanced" financial redress for
OL,8,Fpostmasters who, while not convicted
OL,9,For part of legal action against the
OL,10,FPost Office, made good the apparent
OL,11,Flosses caused by the Horizon system
OL,12,Ffrom their own pockets.
OL,14,FThey will be entitled to a fixed sum
OL,15,Faward of #75,000 through the Horizon
OL,16,FShortfall Scheme, Downing Street said.
